* Entering and Editing Deductions,Inst.Advances,Mid.Advances.
********************************

DO mainprog

*******************
PROCEDURE mainprog
********************

DO iniset
DO UpdDays
DO UpdOthrs
DO UpdBonday
DO DedNewDat
